a.n: Oui-oui, EnquEtes Au Pays Des Jouets

p.d: In Toy Town, someone is distributing gifts to everyone. The toys would love to thank the generous individual but no one knows who it is! Noddy tries to track down the mysterious stranger. Directed by: Albert Pereira-Lazaro (France/USA, 2016) Based on the characters created by Enid Blyton
